
'Raconteur' is a python/pyglet game project. 
It aims to be a character driven turn based RPG, combining on-the-spot gameplay
with generated story arcs.
modulated.

Controls:

Arrow keys  - Movement
B           - Build
Q           - Toggle Build option
M           - Movement by mouse (pathing)
P           - Add new player
T           - Type in name for player
Space       - Put on cloak
R           - Generate random map
Del         - Deletes Map

Right Click - Menu
